Output demo.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 15
Set Width 700
Set Height 380
Set Theme "GitHub Dark"
Set Padding 20
Set TypingSpeed 40ms

Hide
Type "alias c64=c64-demo"
Enter
Type "PS1='$ '"
Enter
Type "clear"
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Show

Type "c64 info"
Enter
Sleep 2.5s

Type "c64 play paradroid.d64"
Enter
Sleep 2.5s

Type "c64 type 'POKE 53280,0'"
Enter
Sleep 2s

Type "c64 info --json"
Enter
Sleep 2.5s
